name: Bibingka Save World! (UCLA Snowjam 2022, Team 7)
description:
Bibingka not sure why Winter capture Summer, Spring, Autumn, but Bibingka want sunny times back! Bibingka with no tan is no Bibingka :( 

Help Bibingka the elf free the seasons from Winter and its evil forces! Blast everything in your path in this silly top-down 2D shooter and become the hero no one asked for :)
